Venizelos Says Wave of Strikes Aimed at Greece’s Democracy

-- B y   M a r i a   P e t r a k i s
-- 
2011-10-14T07:54:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/venizelos-says-wave-of-strikes-aimed-at-greece-s-democracy.html
Greek Finance Minister Evangelos Venizelos said strikes by state workers and occupations of state
buildings presented a situation of complete lawlessness.  These acts strike at the very heart of democracy, Venizelos
told lawmakers in Parliament in  Athens  today, in comments
televised live on state-run Vouli TV. “There are limits,” he
said. “The state must operate.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Petrakis at 
 mpetrakis@bloomberg.net  